Tallinn ni umurwa mukuru, n'umujyi munini wa [[Esitoniya]]. Ni n'umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Harju, intara ituwe cyane na Esitoniya. Iherereye ku nyanja ya Baltique, mu kigobe cya [[Finilande|Finlande]], ituwe n'abaturage bagera ku 450.000<ref>https://andmed.stat.ee/et/stat</ref> mu 2020, ikaba imwe mu murwa mukuru muto w'Uburayi. Tallinn ifite umubare munini wabatangirira kumuntu mubihugu byu Burayi kandi niho havuka amasosiyete mpuzamahanga y’ikoranabuhanga mpuzamahanga, harimo Skype na Transferwise<ref>https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702303734204577464343888754210</ref>. Uyu mujyi wari Umurwa mukuru w’umuco w’iburayi mu 2011, hamwe na Turku muri Finlande.
